messages.messageBody:
"Dry Drowning"

I had never heard of this before. Have you? I felt that this
information was important to share with other parents.

I hope that you will also share this information with friends and
family. It might save a life!

This story talks about 'dry-drowning' which apparently accounts for
10-15% of all drowning in kids.

Here's the link:

http://today. msnbc.msn. com/id/24982210/

Krystal
